{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Popcon Asia 2017, Ajang Silahturami Para Kreator Industri Kreatif Indonesia","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Popcon Asia 2017 yang digelar pada 5-6 Agustus kemarin, masih sukses dan makin sukses menarik perhatian pengunjung! Event berskala internasional ini masih memanjakan pengunjungnya dengan mendatangkan berbagai Pop Stars kenamaan yang tidak asing lagi di bidangnya. Salah satu festival terbesar di Asia Tenggara ini memang bertujuan untuk mengembangkan dan mempromosikan, baik IP ataupun hak kekayaan intelektual kreator Indonesia, ke dunia. Konten-konten yang berkaitan dengan komik, mainan, animasi, industri kreatif dan film ini pun dirilis dan dipamerkan di acara ini. Memang sangat tepat apabila Popcon Asia dikatakan sebagai ajang silahturami para kreator dan penikmat.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13612\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13612\" data-attachment-id=\"13612\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/d/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/d.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Maskot Popcon Asia 2017, Popo, lagi mampir di booth CIAYO Comics.\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Maskot Popcon Asia 2017, Popo, lagi mampir di booth CIAYO Comics.&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/d.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/d.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13612\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/d.png\" alt=\"Maskot Popcon Asia 2017, Popo, lagi mampir di booth CIAYO Comics.\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13612\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Maskot Popcon Asia 2017, Popo, lagi mampir di booth CIAYO Comics.</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Berlangsung si <em>venue</em> hall B Jakarta Convention Centre, <em>venue</em> kali ini terasa lebih besar jika dibandingkan tahun sebelumnya. Hal ini terlihat dari jarak lorong booth kreator yang lebih lapang dan luas, sehingga pengunjung tidak perlu berdesakkan lagi. Masing-masing <em>exhibitor</em> mempunyai<em> activity</em> yang menarik. Berbagai game seru berhadiah merchandise lucu memang sayang untuk dilewati begitu saja.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13639\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13639\" data-attachment-id=\"13639\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/m/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/m.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Jarak antar booth yang lebih lapang dibandingkan sebelumnya.\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Jarak antar booth yang lebih lapang dibandingkan sebelumnya.&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/m.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/m.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13639\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/m.png\" alt=\"Jarak antar booth yang lebih lapang dibandingkan sebelumnya.\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13639\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Jarak antar booth yang lebih lapang dibandingkan sebelumnya.</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CIAYO Comics sebagai salah satu platform komik digital Indonesia di industri kreatif ini pun tak ketinggalan untuk mengisi acara di Popcon Asia 2017. Dengan ide cemerlang membagi-bagikan es krim gratis kepada pengunjung, booth pun ramai dipadati setiap saat. Tak hanya es krim, pengunjung juga dapat mencoba <em>activity</em> seru seperti Fourger <em>shooting range</em>. Jika berhasil membidik di tiga target yang ditentukan, maka peserta berhak untuk membidik target yang berhadiah <em>smartphone</em> dan <em>voucher</em> belanja.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13636\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13636\" data-attachment-id=\"13636\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/l/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/l.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fourger Shooting Range yang banyak diserbu pengunjung, banyak yang penasaran ingin mencobanya.\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Fourger Shooting Range yang banyak diserbu pengunjung, banyak yang penasaran ingin mencobanya.&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/l.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/l.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13636\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/l.png\" alt=\"Fourger Shooting Range yang banyak diserbu pengunjung, banyak yang penasaran ingin mencobanya.\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13636\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Fourger Shooting Range yang banyak diserbu pengunjung, banyak yang penasaran ingin mencobanya.</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Oya, Popcon Asia 2017 juga tak ketinggalan ramai oleh para cosplayer loh. Apalagi cosplayer yang datang di jam-jam tertentu, diberikan akses gratis masuk Popcon! Wah sungguh ide yang sangat menarik. Apalagi dengan ramainya para cosplayer bisa menjadi daya tarik sendiri bagi para pengunjung, karena bisa menjadi target foto bareng! Haha</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13603\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13603\" data-attachment-id=\"13603\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/5-93/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Pasangan cosplayer yang sedang menyantap eskrim dari booth CIAYO Comics.\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Pasangan cosplayer yang sedang menyantap eskrim dari booth CIAYO Comics.&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13603\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5.png\" alt=\"Pasangan cosplayer yang sedang menyantap eskrim dari booth CIAYO Comics.\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13603\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Pasangan cosplayer yang sedang menyantap eskrim dari booth CIAYO Comics.</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13621\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13621\" data-attachment-id=\"13621\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/g/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/g.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Awas hati2, tentara ini sedang patroli di Popcon Asia.\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Awas hati2, tentara ini sedang patroli di Popcon Asia.&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/g.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/g.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13621\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/g.png\" alt=\"Awas hati2, tentara ini sedang patroli di Popcon Asia.\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13621\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Awas hati2, tentara ini sedang patroli di Popcon Asia.</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13615\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13615\" data-attachment-id=\"13615\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/e/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/e.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"e\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/e.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/e.png\" class=\"wp-image-13615 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13615\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Captain Anna Amari, Overwatch by Aileen.</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Penampilan para Pop Stars baik nasional maupun internasional juga mampu meramaikan panggung utama. Terbukti, panggung utama selalu penuh dan petjah dengan pengisi acara. Kehadiran Walter Jones, Peter Sudarso dan Yoshi Sudarso pun sempat membuat para penggemar heboh! Tak ketinggalan, dua aktor asal Jepang pemeran serial legendaris Gavan, Kenji Ohba dan Yuma Ishigaki, pun petjahhh disoraki oleh penonton saat naik ke atas panggung dan mempertontonkan aksi mereka layaknya di film.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13627\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13627\" data-attachment-id=\"13627\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/i/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/i.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"enji Ohba dan Yuma Ishigaki disoraki oleh para penggemarnya saat berada diatas panggung.\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;enji Ohba dan Yuma Ishigaki disoraki oleh para penggemarnya saat berada diatas panggung.&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/i.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/i.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13627\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/i.png\" alt=\"enji Ohba dan Yuma Ishigaki disoraki oleh para penggemarnya saat berada diatas panggung.\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13627\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kenji Ohba dan Yuma Ishigaki disoraki oleh para penggemarnya saat berada diatas panggung.</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Salah satu yang terlihat berbeda dibandingkan tahun sebelumnya adalah, pojok <em>boardgame</em> yang dijadikan satu venue dengan acara panggung utama. Dan area <em>boardgame</em> ini gak pernah sepi loh,  semua meja selalu terisi penuh. Pop Stars juga memiliki area tersendiri untuk bersilahturami dengan penggemarnya. Bagi pengunjung yang ingin berfoto dengan Pop Stars, akan dikenakan sejumlah biaya tertentu.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13588\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13588\" data-attachment-id=\"13588\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/1-117/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-2.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cosplayer cantik ini berkesempatan untuk foto bersama kakak beradik pemeran Power Ranger. Katanya mereka super friendly dan ramah loh! (Sumber: facebook Leenh Hiddleston)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cosplayer cantik ini berkesempatan untuk foto bersama kakak beradik pemeran Power Ranger. Katanya mereka super friendly dan ramah loh! (Sumber: facebook Leenh Hiddleston)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-2.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-2.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13588\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-2.png\" alt=\"Cosplayer cantik ini berkesempatan untuk foto bersama kakak beradik pemeran Power Ranger. Katanya mereka super friendly dan ramah loh! (Sumber: facebook Leenh Hiddleston)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13588\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cosplayer cantik ini berkesempatan untuk foto bersama kakak beradik pemeran Power Ranger. Katanya mereka super friendly dan ramah loh! (Sumber: facebook Leenh Hiddleston)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Datang ke Popcon Asia dapat dipastikan tidak akan pulang dengan tangan kosong. Masing-masing booth biasanya sangat <em>generous</em> membagikan <em>merchandise</em> gratisnya, apalagi di hari kedua. Di booth <em>exhibitor</em> para pelaku indsutri kreatif pun, bisa kita temukan wajah-wajah yang tidak asing lagi. Pada kesempatan ini, Tim CIAYO Blog berhasil mewawancarai Faza Meonk, kreator Juki mengenai Si Juki yang hadir di Popcon, “Di Popcon tahun ini, gue ngerilis komik terbaru Si Juki yang berjudul Si Juki Petualangan di Korea, komik kali ini mengisahkan Si Juki jalan-jalan ke Korea yang berkolaborasi sama Larva. Terus kita juga launching produk barunya dari Si Juki yang bernama SJK.” imbuhnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13618\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13618\" data-attachment-id=\"13618\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/f/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/f.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Faza Meonk, kreator Si Juki, merilis komik terbaru SI Juki jalan-jalan ke Korea di Popcon Asia 2017.\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Faza Meonk, kreator Si Juki, merilis komik terbaru SI Juki jalan-jalan ke Korea di Popcon Asia 2017.&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/f.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/f.png\" class=\"wp-image-13618 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/f.png\" alt=\"Faza Meonk, kreator Si Juki, merilis komik terbaru SI Juki jalan-jalan ke Korea di Popcon Asia 2017.\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13618\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Faza Meonk, kreator Si Juki, merilis komik terbaru SI Juki, petualangan di Korea di Popcon Asia 2017.</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Booth kreator indie memang menjadi ajang pameran para artist lokal. Bahkan tak hanya pameran, beberapa karya pun dijual bahkan didemonstrasikan langsung. Apalagi di hari pertama, Popcon Asia kehadiran Tooru Fujisawa, sang mangaka kenamaan asal Jepang, komikus dari komik manga GTO &#8211; Great Teacher Onizuka.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13630\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13630\" data-attachment-id=\"13630\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/j/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/j.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Booth CIAYO Games di Archipelageek 2017.\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Booth CIAYO Games di Archipelageek 2017.&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/j.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/j.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13630\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/j.png\" alt=\"Booth CIAYO Games di Archipelageek 2017.\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13630\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Booth CIAYO Games di Archipelageek 2017, sekaligus CHIPS: Monster Tap mengumumkan fitur terbarunya yaitu TOURNAMENT.</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dari sisi game, terdapat berbagai pameran game-game lokal buatan developer Indonesia. Pengunjung dapat mencoba memainkan game-game ini. Adapun game <em>upcoming</em> yang belum dirilis yang sudah bisa dimainkan di Popcon Asia. Sebagai salah satu bagian dari industri kreatif, kali ini game didukung oleh BEKRAF (Badan Kreatif Ekonomi Indonesia) dengan menyelenggarakan Archipelageek Popcon Asia 2017. Achipelageek menjaring game-game terbaik asal Indonesia di masing-masing kategori untuk diberi kesempatan memamerkan karyanya gratis! di booth Popcon Asia. Tak ketinggalan, pemenang <em>best mobile games</em> Popcon Awards, CHIPS: Monster Tap oleh CIAYO Games turut membagikan merchandise di booth-nya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13600\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13600\" data-attachment-id=\"13600\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/4-107/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/4.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Bagi-bagi merchandise CHIPS: Monster Tap di booth CIAYO Games.\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Bagi-bagi merchandise CHIPS: Monster Tap di booth CIAYO Games.&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/4.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/4.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13600\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/4.png\" alt=\"Bagi-bagi merchandise CHIPS: Monster Tap di booth CIAYO Games.\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13600\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bagi-bagi merchandise CHIPS: Monster Tap di booth CIAYO Games.</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Di pojok panggung Parade Arena, terdapat berbagai kompetisi seru, seperti turnamen oleh Toge Production, Ultra Space Battle Brawl yang berhadiah keyboard dan mouse gaming Logitech. Ada pun, Pop Make Up Competition, Pop Cosplay Competition, SHF x Popcon Asia Toys Photography Competition, dan Jouchaku Challenge yang menarik perhatian banyak penonton dan partisipan. Oya, launching komik VOLT X Setan Jalanan di CIAYO Comics juga ramai disaksikan di panggung ini. Gimana, uda baca komiknya? Belum, silahkan baca komik- komik keren nya <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/comic/volt-x-setan-jalanan\">disini</a>,</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13609\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13609\" data-attachment-id=\"13609\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/7-55/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-1.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Volt X Setan Jalanan launching di Popcon Asia 2017.\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-1.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-1.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13609\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-1.png\" alt=\"Volt X Setan Jalanan launching di Popcon Asia 2017.\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13609\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Volt X Setan Jalanan launching di Popcon Asia 2017.</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Meski para pengunjung tidak membuka booth, namun mereka juga turut berkontribusi besar di industri kreatif karena membeli karya kreator yang tentunya sebagai bentuk apresiasi. Apalah arti kreator tanpa penikmat? Bu Grace Kusnadi, selaku <em>co-founder</em> sekaligus <em>event director</em> dari Popcon Asia, mengatakan bahwa konsep yang diusung Popcon Asia tahun ini adalah kolaborasi, “Tema Popcon tahun ini kita ingin mengangkat semua kolaborasi yang sudah ada. Dari film ke komik, dari komik ke musik, dari game ke komik.” Kata Grace Kusnadi saat diwawancari oleh Tim CIAYO Blog. “Saya senang sekali dari teknologi yang ikut, dari platform-platform yang bisa bantu kreator untuk lebih menaikkan karyanya, menjual karyanya, memperkenalkan karyanya. Karena sekarang tanpa teknologi, kita nggak bisa maju yah.” tambahnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13651\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13651\" data-attachment-id=\"13651\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/b.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Grace Kusniadi, co-founder dan event director Popcon Asia, saat diwawancarai oleh Tim CIAYO Blog.\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Grace Kusniadi, co-founder dan event director Popcon Asia, saat diwawancarai oleh Tim CIAYO Blog.&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/b.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/b.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13651\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/b.png\" alt=\"Grace Kusniadi, co-founder dan event director Popcon Asia, saat diwawancarai oleh Tim CIAYO Blog.\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13651\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Grace Kusnadi, co-founder dan event director Popcon Asia, saat diwawancarai oleh Tim CIAYO Blog.</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kesuksesan Popcon Asia tahun ini tentu menambah antisipasi kita, kira-kira apalagi yang akan ditawarkan oleh Popcon Asia di tahun berikutnya?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13624\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13624\" data-attachment-id=\"13624\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popcon-asia-2017-ajang-silahturami-para-kreator-industri-kreatif-indonesia/attachment/h/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/h.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Yul, download aplikasi CIAYO Comics di playstore and appstore.\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Yul, download aplikasi CIAYO Comics di playstore and appstore.&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/h.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/h.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13624\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/h.png\" alt=\"Yul, download aplikasi CIAYO Comics di playstore and appstore.\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13624\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Yul, download aplikasi CIAYO Comics di playstore and appstore.</p></div></p>\n"}},"pageCont